*Logged In
A minimalistic workout tracker built with HTML, CSS and Javascript
**Features
-Track upper and lower body workouts
-Record date, weight and reps
-View workout history grouped by date and exercise
-Sort workout history by newest or oldest
-Edit and delete sets
-Responsive layout for desktop and mobile
***Current Limitations
-Data is stored only in the browser
-Exercises are currently predefined in the code
View the app here -> https://logged-in-eight.vercel.app/
